creator: E. Louise Smythe
description:
LibriVox recording of A Primary Reader: Old-time Stories, Fairy Tales and Myths Retold by Children by E. Louise Smythe.

Read in English by Sarah Jennings and Abby.

This is a book of simple, classic stories for beginning readers. It is included in Year 1 of the Ambleside reading list. There are short lists of reading words on each page, and these have been read by a child. - Summary by Sarah Jennings

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
subject: librivox; audiobooks;young children; ambleside; easy reading
